_______________________________________________________________________________
"Lend Health"      
        This allows the psionicist to lend some of his life energy
        over to another person.  It's not healing, it is rather a
        transfer of wounds.  It restores 10 hp to the target.
 
SP Cost:  15 / 10 HPs	Guild Level:  2		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  lendh <target>
